{"tid":187812,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣無能力成家立室","createTime":"2017-04-05T08:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T15:05:52.000Z","uid":83913,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"668b3a8dd4320da043a836f75c50c8cd89b52f63","tid":187812,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:35:07.000Z","msg":"前任女朋友我真係好愛，<br />\n<br />\n但無奈必須要放手<br />\n<br />\n因為最基本既一個家我都俾唔到佢，<br />\n<br />\n未來十年都無信心買到樓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢好鍾意小朋友，<br />\n<br />\n但我絕對唔會係今時今日既香港生小朋友<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係害咗個小朋友<br />\n<br />\n於是我就無奈地放手&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我真係好廢好無力，但鍾意一個人會想佢得到幸福，既然我真係無能力俾到佢一個穩定既家，只好放佢走<br />\n<br />\n巴打，盡情屌我垃圾屌我廢啦，生於香港窮人家庭真係賤過地底泥，我呢啲垃圾渣滓有咩資格拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4804b93c5fcdc8cb67119bc788389967b307e2cc","tid":187812,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:35:46.000Z","msg":"香港大把人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9985499dc52c65f6690f8063cf815eacd51842e2","tid":187812,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:35:58.000Z","msg":"我垃圾我廢物無出息命賤死撚咗都唔抵可憐"},{"pid":"88f5ea1d4be8f7280f7f77eb68921182681b1b66","tid":187812,"uid":15572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:38:04.000Z","msg":"睇你點睇，其實好多人唔洗搵好多錢都有個家庭，有仔女，不過當然過既生活可能無咁奢侈，但一樣過得好開心，心中富足嘛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw加油巴打"},{"pid":"78edf9c8d11bb5026f59ab87a22441fda04a4d0e","tid":187812,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:38:48.000Z","msg":"一諗返起同佢一齊既經歷，到無奈分手果種痛<br />\n<br />\n忍唔住喊住咁用指甲扯自己d皮<br />\n<br />\n我有資格愛人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74dc66a1221e77838a6a5590793645cd0ba3f95","tid":187812,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我垃圾我廢物無出息命賤死撚咗都唔抵可憐</blockquote><br />\n好醜命生成，冇辦法嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13a99eb5a46ed65b03ee0b018a88b49de66f5f9","tid":187812,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:46:44.000Z","msg":"拍拖咁耐我都無乜點帶你去食好野<br />\n<br />\n出親街活動都唔敢點洗錢<br />\n<br />\n多得你肯挨，<br />\n<br />\n但搵到個肯挨既女友，先更加唔想你要陪我挨<br />\n<br />\n你每挨一次我個心就痛一次"},{"pid":"974631d90e4d292532c73dbf4f5c4f203311ab44","tid":187812,"uid":81463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你幾多歲呀?"},{"pid":"39ccb1abd676541e6019d421380957a28b26f559","tid":187812,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:01:51.000Z","msg":"香港地有邊個會買到樓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1e6eaf4951ac3323ce7136aae42772b30faa2d","tid":187812,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:03:22.000Z","msg":"大家唔match啫 屌你咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bb97232656cc229b01cf033ebdfce3347abb8c","tid":187812,"uid":74911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:06:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"fa4dfabb6fed7030f481aa5b5e556a31526d6e86","tid":187812,"uid":5047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:07:58.000Z","msg":"人地都無嫌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9eddbb6465c68877b9c5c993433f14e7c18f928","tid":187812,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家唔match啫 屌你咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我反而好想有人大大力屌我<br />\n<br />\n屋企人都怪我俾一個咁好既&quot;媳婦&quot;走咗<br />\n<br />\n但真係有苦自己知<br />\n<br />\n又唔怪得屋企人既佢哋都供到我大學"},{"pid":"237e37c16f96baef10bdbd82a1f371248949d623","tid":187812,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:12:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港地有邊個會買到樓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實真心好多，我指屋企有樓果d起碼可以同屋企住。<br />\n<br />\n而我屋企租樓住，我要夾租同照顧兩老，<br />\n<br />\n真係有d吃力"},{"pid":"8e40767618f569a4a4eaa80d3d6c027ed2d5721a","tid":187812,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你幾多歲呀?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nu grad2年度"},{"pid":"c633eda570c53d687d256189035a60db887b6098","tid":187812,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地都無嫌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有既，成日都有意無意話好想搬出去住<br />\n<br />\n又話好想生小朋友"},{"pid":"2fdf984a3a36e13baeebb4f43a44e81309495c0b","tid":187812,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/81xybrva\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F81xybrva&h=b6d1ded0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱咬完自己一輪，我要自己永遠都記得呢種痛<br />\n<br />\n咁以後先會知道自己出人頭地之前無資格愛人<br />\n<br />\n我真係對你唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79327924785d48b76e1f531426e10e60a1d3ea7b","tid":187812,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:49:45.000Z","msg":"男人老狗喊到成個女人咁<br />\n<br />\n但除咗喊之外咩都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9aaf41fcc99f6194d6d6ade35a7366ffc9c985","tid":187812,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"人貴自知"},{"pid":"948ef50fd801121401efcf6a68609e0748301f1f","tid":187812,"uid":2781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:15:05.000Z","msg":"唔係你嘅錯"},{"pid":"591e7fb96608059ff4f719bfd90038cb7cd43c40","tid":187812,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍拖咁耐我都無乜點帶你去食好野<br />\n<br />\n出親街活動都唔敢點洗錢<br />\n<br />\n多得你肯挨，<br />\n<br />\n但搵到個肯挨既女友，先更加唔想你要陪我挨<br />\n<br />\n你每挨一次我個心就痛一次</blockquote><br />\n點解我之前條仔唔識咁諗<br />\n捱捱下變左理所當然"},{"pid":"4d965976403f38d84e2b4cf034c29579dc852a4d","tid":187812,"uid":34160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"佢知唔知你因為呢個原因分手"},{"pid":"a3468218cdde92719f9c09e400a39980ca717e9b","tid":187812,"uid":32063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"點解我覺得你好似個小朋友咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99757bc2dde341df55f09acd1b1b8b7123bf421b","tid":187812,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解我覺得你好似個小朋友咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我明你講咩<br />\n<br />\n但係呢件事上面，我真係無力到好似個小朋友咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb7c5006584bec8236e903077a11646c28c710b","tid":187812,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢知唔知你因為呢個原因分手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢大概都知同明，<br />\n<br />\n因為其實都講過現階段我真係俾唔到承諾佢，短期內都唔會有好轉<br />\n<br />\n女人青春太寶貴，我希望佢唔好冒險"}]}